WEBVTT

00:00:01.503 --> 00:00:03.273
[NARRATOR]
Last Dragon Ball Z Kai--

00:00:03.306 --> 00:00:05.845
When a dazzling
Times Twenty Kaio-ken

00:00:05.878 --> 00:00:08.217
did little more
than irritate Frieza,

00:00:08.250 --> 00:00:12.190
Goku quickly found
himself in dire straits.

00:00:14.763 --> 00:00:17.602
[FRIEZA] Stop talking
nonsense and make this fun!

00:00:17.635 --> 00:00:19.573
I have to win...

00:00:19.606 --> 00:00:22.478
I owe it to too many
people not to lose...

00:00:22.512 --> 00:00:24.783
Don't toy with me!

00:00:25.986 --> 00:00:36.172
♪ Opening Song ♪

00:02:02.979 --> 00:02:04.516
[FRIEZA] What?!

00:02:11.663 --> 00:02:12.732
[FREIZA] Filthy...

00:02:12.765 --> 00:02:14.468
Presumptuous...

00:02:14.503 --> 00:02:16.172
Imbecile!

00:02:22.719 --> 00:02:25.290
[FRIEZA] That rather
caught me off guard.

00:02:25.324 --> 00:02:29.566
Is it safe to say someone's
got their fight back?

00:02:31.469 --> 00:02:33.941
[groan]

00:02:33.974 --> 00:02:35.578
[FRIEZA] Too bad
there's still the whole

00:02:35.612 --> 00:02:38.617
"Saiyan" thing
working against you.

00:02:39.986 --> 00:02:44.495
[FRIEZA] Lower life forms
are so easy to anticipate.

00:02:44.529 --> 00:02:48.670
Right down to their
last desperate bid to live.

00:02:53.246 --> 00:02:57.688
[chuckles]

00:02:59.827 --> 00:03:01.830
[chuckles]

00:03:02.198 --> 00:03:07.542
[GOKU gasps of pain]

00:03:12.685 --> 00:03:16.092
[heavy breathing]

00:03:16.126 --> 00:03:18.897
[chuckle]

00:03:18.931 --> 00:03:20.467
Ah!

00:03:29.118 --> 00:03:35.799
[GOKU struggling]

00:03:35.832 --> 00:03:38.771
[FRIEZA] Ready to
throw in the towel yet?

00:03:41.910 --> 00:03:43.146
[FRIEZA chuckling]

00:03:43.179 --> 00:03:47.187
Would death be a
welcome reprieve?

00:03:47.220 --> 00:03:49.926
Heh... That would
be simple, too.

00:03:49.960 --> 00:03:54.736
[heaving breathing]

00:03:54.770 --> 00:03:56.807
I can't take this...

00:03:56.841 --> 00:03:58.510
No, I'm gonna help--

00:03:58.544 --> 00:03:59.445
No!

00:03:59.478 --> 00:04:02.619
Piccolo! Dad'll
die if I don't!

00:04:02.652 --> 00:04:06.560
Just wait! He's got
something up his sleeve!

00:04:06.593 --> 00:04:08.731
[PICCOLO] He's got so
little power left, though,

00:04:08.764 --> 00:04:10.936
the question is what?

00:04:10.969 --> 00:04:18.851
[GOKU heavy breathing]

00:04:18.884 --> 00:04:20.453
Oh my...

00:04:20.487 --> 00:04:22.291
What are you up to?

00:04:22.324 --> 00:04:32.545
[GOKU even breathing]

00:04:36.119 --> 00:04:37.922
[gasp] A Spirit Bomb!

00:04:37.956 --> 00:04:40.327
Huh...?
A Spirit Bomb?

00:04:40.360 --> 00:04:42.164
Uh, yeah...
That's right...

00:04:42.197 --> 00:04:44.302
It's a special last-ditch
move Goku picked up

00:04:44.335 --> 00:04:46.439
during his training
regimen with King Kai...

00:04:46.472 --> 00:04:48.143
[KRILLIN] See, he
gathers all the energy

00:04:48.176 --> 00:04:49.312
from the things
around him:

00:04:49.345 --> 00:04:51.282
grass, trees, even us!

00:04:51.315 --> 00:04:53.754
Everything down to the
tiniest Namekian microbe.

00:04:53.788 --> 00:04:56.660
Basically he uses anything
around him with a life force.

00:04:56.693 --> 00:04:58.964
Then he condenses it
into a giant ball of energy,

00:04:58.998 --> 00:05:02.138
and presto! You've got
yourself a Spirit Bomb.

00:05:02.171 --> 00:05:05.310
Ha. Well... Lucky him...

00:05:05.343 --> 00:05:07.381
Guess King Kai
didn't teach us that.

00:05:07.414 --> 00:05:09.786
So... But...
I-- I mean, how...?

00:05:09.819 --> 00:05:12.224
This place...
Well... it doesn't have

00:05:12.258 --> 00:05:13.561
all that much life, right?

00:05:13.594 --> 00:05:15.497
Where's the energy
gonna come from?

00:05:15.531 --> 00:05:17.167
How should I know...?!

00:05:17.201 --> 00:05:18.269
But just look down there.

00:05:18.303 --> 00:05:20.239
He doesn't have
a lot of choices...

00:05:20.273 --> 00:05:21.577
Plus, he knows
a lot more about it

00:05:21.610 --> 00:05:23.313
than any of us do. So...

00:05:23.346 --> 00:05:25.651
Maybe he can
make it work.

00:05:32.297 --> 00:05:33.801
[GOKU ] I can't
believe I'm doing this.

00:05:33.835 --> 00:05:36.640
A Spirit Bomb's the last
thing I wanted to use.

00:05:36.674 --> 00:05:39.579
If I mess up, there's no
guarantee it won't split

00:05:39.613 --> 00:05:41.750
Planet Namek
right down the middle.

00:05:43.487 --> 00:05:45.390
[GOKU] If I don't hit
Frieza with everything

00:05:45.424 --> 00:05:47.060
I've got, though, it's
just a matter of time

00:05:47.093 --> 00:05:49.799
before he has the whole
universe in a choke-hold.

00:05:49.833 --> 00:05:52.370
I have to try something,
even if it's drastic.

00:05:52.404 --> 00:05:55.644
Whether it works out exactly
how I need it to or not.

00:05:56.646 --> 00:06:06.132
♪

00:06:06.165 --> 00:06:08.737
Come on... What is this?

00:06:08.771 --> 00:06:11.209
Bravely drudging
up more nonsense

00:06:11.242 --> 00:06:12.779
for me to contend with?

00:06:12.812 --> 00:06:15.384
[FRIEZA] Heh! What could
you conceivably have left

00:06:15.417 --> 00:06:17.555
in your weakened state?

00:06:20.126 --> 00:06:21.997
Oh man.

00:06:22.699 --> 00:06:25.103
Goku, do you really
think a Spirit Bomb's

00:06:25.136 --> 00:06:27.040
gonna be what
does the trick?

00:06:32.518 --> 00:06:35.490
[FRIEZA] I don't get
it. What is he doing?

00:06:35.525 --> 00:06:39.833
Why would he stand there
essentially motionless?

00:06:39.866 --> 00:06:43.741
[GOKU] I call upon the
grasses. I call upon the trees.

00:06:43.775 --> 00:06:45.912
I call upon every
single living thing

00:06:45.945 --> 00:06:48.951
that either crawls,
slinks, slithers, or swims

00:06:48.984 --> 00:06:50.320
on this planet;

00:06:50.353 --> 00:06:53.994
on this planet, and in
the entire universe!

00:06:54.629 --> 00:07:04.649
♪

00:07:21.382 --> 00:07:23.554
[GOKU] That's it.
Just a tiny bit of energy

00:07:23.587 --> 00:07:25.691
from each of
you is all I need.

00:07:25.725 --> 00:07:27.093
Any neighboring
worlds out there

00:07:27.127 --> 00:07:30.133
that don't want to see
Frieza win this fight,

00:07:30.167 --> 00:07:31.803
help me defeat him!

00:07:31.836 --> 00:07:35.778
Help me create a Spirit Bomb!

00:07:35.811 --> 00:07:45.831
♪

00:08:14.321 --> 00:08:21.536
[GOKU struggling]

00:08:29.485 --> 00:08:31.322
[gasp]

00:08:31.356 --> 00:08:33.426
Wha-- What
is that...?

00:08:33.459 --> 00:08:35.263
What am
I sensing?

00:08:35.297 --> 00:08:36.833
Like I said, it--

00:08:40.775 --> 00:08:43.213
The... The Spirit Bomb!

00:08:43.246 --> 00:08:44.281
[gasp]

00:08:44.314 --> 00:08:46.386
[trembling]

00:08:46.419 --> 00:08:47.722
But...

00:08:47.756 --> 00:08:49.793
That can't be it...!

00:08:49.826 --> 00:08:52.999
[KRILLIN]
That-- That's gigantic!

00:08:53.032 --> 00:09:03.018
♪

00:09:15.210 --> 00:09:19.385
[GOKU struggling]

00:09:19.418 --> 00:09:20.888
Hm...

00:09:27.101 --> 00:09:29.104
It's... It's just...

00:09:29.138 --> 00:09:30.775
...impossibly huge!

00:09:30.808 --> 00:09:32.678
So then this
one's exceptional.

00:09:32.712 --> 00:09:35.216
[GOHAN] The one on Earth
was only about this size...

00:09:35.249 --> 00:09:36.854
[KRILLIN] Yeah I know,
but that one there's

00:09:36.887 --> 00:09:39.491
gotta be at least
fifty yards in diameter.

00:09:40.126 --> 00:09:42.531
He shouldn't have been
able to make one that big.

00:09:42.565 --> 00:09:43.734
Not from the life
force he would have

00:09:43.768 --> 00:09:45.604
gathered from around here.

00:09:45.638 --> 00:09:47.508
I think Goku must
be collecting energy

00:09:47.542 --> 00:09:49.880
from everywhere in
the entire universe!

00:09:49.913 --> 00:09:51.583
Well, from
the looks of things,

00:09:51.617 --> 00:09:53.486
Frieza hasn't
caught on yet...

00:09:53.520 --> 00:09:55.323
Why doesn't Goku
just use the thing now

00:09:55.356 --> 00:09:56.693
while he's got
a good shot?

00:09:56.726 --> 00:09:58.496
Maybe... to finish Frieza off

00:09:58.530 --> 00:10:00.634
it'll have to be
even bigger than that.

00:10:00.668 --> 00:10:02.104
It's the only reason
I can think that

00:10:02.137 --> 00:10:03.339
Goku would have to wait.

00:10:03.373 --> 00:10:05.176
He doesn't have
much longer...!

00:10:05.210 --> 00:10:07.047
Come on...! Hit him, Dad!

00:10:07.080 --> 00:10:09.418
[GOKU] That's it.
Keep it coming.

00:10:09.451 --> 00:10:11.823
Just a little more...

00:10:11.856 --> 00:10:21.876
♪

00:10:27.956 --> 00:10:28.790
Amateur...

00:10:28.824 --> 00:10:32.231
You're obviously
just stalling...

00:10:32.264 --> 00:10:33.667
Make a move.

00:10:33.700 --> 00:10:35.637
Or is this ridiculous
pose meant to

00:10:35.671 --> 00:10:38.476
signify your
unconditional surrender?

00:10:38.510 --> 00:10:39.612
[GOKU] The time
it's taking to gather

00:10:39.646 --> 00:10:41.215
all the energy
this thing needs

00:10:41.248 --> 00:10:42.952
is leaving me wide open.

00:10:42.985 --> 00:10:46.325
Please... don't let
him figure that out!

00:10:59.686 --> 00:11:04.295
[heavy breathing]

00:11:04.328 --> 00:11:11.709
[GOKU struggling]

00:11:11.743 --> 00:11:13.613
Ugh. This is beyond
preposterous...!

00:11:13.647 --> 00:11:16.218
How long do you intend
to just stand there?!

00:11:16.252 --> 00:11:19.257
[GOKU] You know, that's
a very good question.

00:11:19.291 --> 00:11:21.796
[chuckle]

00:11:25.638 --> 00:11:27.373
Ape!

00:11:34.221 --> 00:11:35.591
Oh no! He caught on!

00:11:35.624 --> 00:11:38.062
No, Krillin...
I don't think so.

00:11:38.930 --> 00:11:44.374
[heavy breathing]

00:11:44.408 --> 00:11:46.078
I'm very sorry about that.

00:11:46.111 --> 00:11:49.184
I must've interrupted
your concentration.

00:11:52.156 --> 00:11:55.764
[GOKU chuckling]

00:11:55.797 --> 00:11:58.770
Errrm. Is this some
kind of joke to you?!

00:12:02.443 --> 00:12:04.482
[GOKU chuckle]

00:12:04.516 --> 00:12:06.285
Eeeeeya!

00:12:13.701 --> 00:12:15.369
[ALL gasp]

00:12:18.409 --> 00:12:21.048
[low growl]

00:12:24.321 --> 00:12:26.759
[GOKU] Almost there...

00:12:27.795 --> 00:12:30.968
I'm not going
to ask you again.

00:12:34.709 --> 00:12:37.213
[chuckle]

00:12:39.284 --> 00:12:42.457
[growl]

00:12:47.668 --> 00:12:48.904
How much
can he stand?

00:12:48.938 --> 00:12:49.906
We've gotta help him!

00:12:49.940 --> 00:12:51.242
Gohan! Krillin! Now!

00:12:51.275 --> 00:12:53.747
Transfer whatever power
you can spare to me!

00:12:53.780 --> 00:12:54.683
[BOTH] Huh?

00:12:54.716 --> 00:12:56.620
Quickly...
There's no time!

00:12:56.653 --> 00:12:58.188
Right...

00:13:06.807 --> 00:13:11.048
[wheezing chuckles]

00:13:11.081 --> 00:13:13.286
What's the big rush, Frieza?

00:13:13.319 --> 00:13:15.724
You're so impatient...

00:13:15.757 --> 00:13:19.465
You dare
mock me... Ape?

00:13:19.498 --> 00:13:20.867
Ahhh!

00:13:20.901 --> 00:13:25.844
Aaahhh...!

00:13:30.386 --> 00:13:32.959
[PICCOLO] Pay no attention
to what's going on down there!

00:13:32.992 --> 00:13:34.361
Focus your energy!

00:13:34.394 --> 00:13:35.597
[GOHAN] Okay!

00:13:38.537 --> 00:13:45.216
[heavy breathing]

00:13:46.820 --> 00:13:48.089
I've never fully understood

00:13:48.122 --> 00:13:50.459
the Saiyan thought process...

00:13:50.493 --> 00:13:52.931
Nor do I ever expect to...

00:13:53.967 --> 00:13:56.438
Such an unpleasant species.

00:13:57.942 --> 00:13:59.812
This pathetic
excuse for a battle

00:13:59.845 --> 00:14:02.685
has carried on quite
long enough, I think...

00:14:02.719 --> 00:14:03.887
It's time I dealt with you

00:14:03.920 --> 00:14:06.893
and this planet
in one fell swoop.

00:14:08.096 --> 00:14:11.001
Alas, this includes your
little monkey child too.

00:14:11.034 --> 00:14:13.473
With him, the Saiyan
scourge will be wiped

00:14:13.507 --> 00:14:15.510
from this universe entirely.

00:14:15.544 --> 00:14:18.082
[FRIEZA chuckle] Proving
the fabled Super Saiyan

00:14:18.115 --> 00:14:21.656
was just that: a fable.

00:14:22.858 --> 00:14:24.394
[gasp]

00:14:27.935 --> 00:14:29.539
[FRIEZA] That's no sun!

00:14:29.572 --> 00:14:31.108
What the--?!

00:14:37.988 --> 00:14:39.559
No. Damn it!

00:14:39.592 --> 00:14:40.561
Is tha--

00:14:40.594 --> 00:14:42.665
Is that what
I think it is?!

00:14:43.265 --> 00:14:47.006
I've never seen a mass
of energy that size!

00:14:48.375 --> 00:14:51.248
[FRIEZA] That's
what he was doing!

00:14:54.689 --> 00:14:56.158
[PICCOLO] Good. Enough.

00:14:56.191 --> 00:14:59.097
Save a little bit of
energy for yourselves.

00:14:59.733 --> 00:15:00.667
[GOHAN] All right...

00:15:00.700 --> 00:15:02.605
Frieza's wise to Goku's ploy.

00:15:02.638 --> 00:15:04.141
You two... Listen up...!

00:15:04.174 --> 00:15:06.178
Whatever happens,
you just stay put!

00:15:06.211 --> 00:15:08.449
I forbid you to
interfere in any way!

00:15:08.482 --> 00:15:11.022
He was forging that
thing right over my head

00:15:11.055 --> 00:15:12.457
and I had no idea...!

00:15:12.490 --> 00:15:15.864
How was he able to dredge
up that much power?!

00:15:15.897 --> 00:15:17.968
[GOKU] Ugh. It's all over now.

00:15:18.001 --> 00:15:19.839
Even if this Spirit
Bomb was strong enough

00:15:19.872 --> 00:15:21.108
to take Frieza down...

00:15:21.142 --> 00:15:22.210
...now that he's seen it,

00:15:22.244 --> 00:15:24.447
I've lost the
element of surprise.

00:15:25.483 --> 00:15:28.489
Ha! You were going to
blindside me with that...?

00:15:28.523 --> 00:15:29.859
How unfortunate.

00:15:29.893 --> 00:15:32.130
Don't you hate it when
a plan falls apart...?

00:15:32.163 --> 00:15:34.267
I know I certainly do.

00:15:40.313 --> 00:15:41.516
[chuckles]

00:15:41.549 --> 00:15:42.951
Nice try.

00:15:45.725 --> 00:15:47.260
No!

00:15:49.364 --> 00:15:50.534
Farewell.

00:15:51.503 --> 00:15:52.638
Huh?

00:15:55.510 --> 00:15:58.215
[FRIEZA yell]

00:16:02.323 --> 00:16:02.892
Piccolo?

00:16:02.925 --> 00:16:04.027
Yeah, yeah...

00:16:04.060 --> 00:16:05.598
Just hurry and finish
that Spirit Bomb

00:16:05.631 --> 00:16:06.900
before he comes back!

00:16:06.933 --> 00:16:08.536
I owe you one.

00:16:12.443 --> 00:16:16.853
[GOKU groaning]

00:16:16.887 --> 00:16:18.790
[PICCOLO] Hey, you
better make it fast

00:16:18.824 --> 00:16:20.159
because that
sneak attack was really

00:16:20.193 --> 00:16:22.097
the best I could
manage right now...

00:16:22.130 --> 00:16:23.498
[GOKU] You got it!

00:16:34.320 --> 00:16:36.926
How is that Namekian
still drawing breath?!

00:16:36.959 --> 00:16:40.199
I thought they'd
all been taken care of!

00:16:48.650 --> 00:16:58.670
[GOKU groaning]

00:17:08.489 --> 00:17:12.297
I'm beset on all sides by
sneaking, parasitic flies...!

00:17:12.330 --> 00:17:15.102
This is more
than I can stand!

00:17:22.818 --> 00:17:24.421
Goku! Hurry it up!

00:17:24.454 --> 00:17:26.792
How much longer do you
need to finish that thing?

00:17:26.826 --> 00:17:29.231
[PICCOLO]I hate to rush
you, but something tells me

00:17:29.264 --> 00:17:31.034
Frieza's losing his patience.

00:17:31.067 --> 00:17:32.470
I'm... sorry...

00:17:32.505 --> 00:17:35.443
I just need a little
bit more time!

00:17:35.476 --> 00:17:38.216
Ugh... Just throw it already!

00:17:38.249 --> 00:17:40.253
No! It's not done yet!

00:17:40.286 --> 00:17:41.889
[GOKU] It's still too weak!

00:17:41.923 --> 00:17:48.570
[groaning]

00:17:48.603 --> 00:17:58.623
♪

00:18:06.706 --> 00:18:09.010
Hmm... Too pesky to live...?

00:18:09.043 --> 00:18:11.582
Ah... But too stubborn to die.

00:18:11.615 --> 00:18:12.483
So you say...

00:18:12.517 --> 00:18:14.822
You're gonna eat
those words, scum!

00:18:14.855 --> 00:18:16.124
What's he doing?

00:18:16.157 --> 00:18:18.930
I think he's gonna try
to sacrifice himself...

00:18:19.497 --> 00:18:21.401
I mean... He really
can't have all that much

00:18:21.434 --> 00:18:24.642
power left after
the move he just pulled.

00:18:27.113 --> 00:18:29.250
Goku isn't finished
making the Spirit Bomb yet,

00:18:29.284 --> 00:18:32.123
so I think Piccolo's
engaging Frieza in a one-on-one

00:18:32.157 --> 00:18:34.394
just to buy him some time.

00:18:35.463 --> 00:18:36.967
No he's not!

00:18:37.000 --> 00:18:38.503
[KRILLIN] Gohan, wait!

00:18:47.755 --> 00:18:51.394
Goku... Please hurry...

00:18:54.267 --> 00:19:02.617
[PICCOLO growls]

00:19:08.195 --> 00:19:11.135
Well... That
didn't do any good.

00:19:11.168 --> 00:19:12.771
[growl]

00:19:21.455 --> 00:19:25.797
Arrrhhh!

00:19:29.672 --> 00:19:36.852
[heavy breathing]

00:19:44.935 --> 00:19:46.471
Hmmm...

00:19:48.142 --> 00:19:52.150
Ahhh!

00:19:52.183 --> 00:19:56.224
How can someone so
resilient be so dumb?

00:19:58.195 --> 00:20:01.468
Unless they have a death wish!

00:20:04.675 --> 00:20:08.282
[PICCOLO] We're officially
at the end of our rope, Goku!

00:20:08.315 --> 00:20:12.624
Fi-- Finish the
damn Spirit Bomb!

00:20:16.933 --> 00:20:18.603
[GOKU] I can't...

00:20:25.717 --> 00:20:31.494
[heavy breathing]

00:20:34.735 --> 00:20:36.772
Aaahhh!

00:20:45.022 --> 00:20:49.363
[PICCOLO groaning]

00:20:54.842 --> 00:20:56.746
That's all I've got...

00:20:56.779 --> 00:21:00.787
Please tell me you're
almost done with that thing...

00:21:01.823 --> 00:21:03.827
It's not finished yet...

00:21:03.860 --> 00:21:06.098
[GOKU] Ugh. If I
throw it at Frieza now,

00:21:06.131 --> 00:21:08.068
it won't do any good!

00:21:12.945 --> 00:21:15.115
Hmmm. Try as I might,

00:21:15.149 --> 00:21:17.855
I can't think of a
reason to spare you.

00:21:17.955 --> 00:21:20.693
[trembling]

00:21:22.129 --> 00:21:23.866
[NARRATOR]
Just moments shy of the

00:21:23.900 --> 00:21:25.604
Spirit Bomb's completion,

00:21:25.637 --> 00:21:29.144
events have taken an even
more desperate turn...

00:21:29.177 --> 00:21:30.714
Can Piccolo be saved?

00:21:30.747 --> 00:21:33.953
Find out, next
Dragon Ball Z Kai!

00:21:34.889 --> 00:21:44.875
♪ Closing Song ♪

00:22:38.415 --> 00:22:39.718
[GOKU] Hey! It's me, Goku!

00:22:39.751 --> 00:22:41.287
Wow, we really
came through that

00:22:41.321 --> 00:22:42.590
by the skin of our teeth!

00:22:42.624 --> 00:22:43.626
[KRILLIN] This
means we can finally

00:22:43.659 --> 00:22:45.262
set a course for
home, right?

00:22:45.296 --> 00:22:46.966
I think I'm
ready to settle down,

00:22:46.999 --> 00:22:48.068
if you know what I mean.

00:22:48.101 --> 00:22:49.371
[GOKU laughing]

00:22:49.404 --> 00:22:51.842
Uhh... Wait...! Oh no!

00:22:51.875 --> 00:22:54.881
Next time, on
Dragon Ball Z Kai:

00:22:58.690 --> 00:23:03.566
[KRILLIN]
Help me...! Goku!

